<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_326" id="162v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_326_r2l1"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Preyſing<ex>er</ex></expan> geſeʒʒen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l2">cʒü varndorf / . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_326_r2l3"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>richtıgu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l4"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / als <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hochgeborn fürſt vnd <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Ernſt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l5">Beyrn vnſer <expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / ew mit vns gericht hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l6">vnd alle die mit ew <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dacht</expan> <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein / <expan>Awſgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l7"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Snel / . Alſo ſprechen ew etlich cʒü / ob ſie auch in der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l8">richtigung ſein / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l9">vnd <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr erberkeit wiſſen / daʒ vvir auch <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> nicht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l10">wiſſen / . <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Ernſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l11">die richtigung gemachet hab mit ew vnd allen den / die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l12">
<del rend="strikethrough">d </del> mit ew <expan>dary<ex>n</ex>ne</expan> verdacht <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l13">Awſgenomen des Snellen / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ṽ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Bartholo<ex>me</ex>ȷ</expan> xȷ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_326_r2l14">Anno etc vndecimo / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_326" id="162v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Preysing<ex>er</ex></expan>, gesezzen czü Varndorf</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>richtigu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hochgeborn
                        fürst und <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ernst <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Beyrn,
                        unser <expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, ew mit uns gericht hat und alle, die mit ew
                                <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dacht</expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, <expan>awsgenome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Snel, also sprechen ew etlich czü, ob sie auch
                        in der richtigung sein, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr
                        erberkeit wissen, daz wir auch <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> nicht wissen,
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> daz <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ernst, die
                        richtigung gemachet hab mit ew und allen, den die mit ew
                                <expan>dary<ex>n</ex>ne</expan> verdacht
                            <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> sein
                        <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>, awsgenomen des Snellen.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Bartholo<ex>me</ex>i</expan> xi anno etc. undecimo.</ab>
</div>
